<view class="container">
  <view class="content">
    <view class="guide-card">
      <view class="header">
        <text class="title">样品邮寄说明</text>
        <text class="subtitle">您的检测号：{{detectionId || '—'}}</text>
      </view>

      <view class="section">
        <view class="section-title">样品准备要求</view>
        <view class="section-block">
          <view class="item-title">🐝 蜜蜂样品</view>
          <view class="item-text">• 死亡成蜂20-30只，选择新鲜死亡样品</view>
          <view class="item-text">• 使用密封袋装，防止泄露</view>
        </view>
        <view class="section-block">
          <view class="item-title">🍯 幼虫样品</view>
          <view class="item-text">• 含巢脾的病死幼虫 5-10 个巢房</view>
          <view class="item-text">• 冷藏保存，尽快邮寄</view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="section">
        <view class="section-title">邮寄地址</view>
        <view class="address-card">
          <view>🏢 蜜蜂疫病检测中心</view>
          <view>📍 北京市朝阳区xxx路xxx号</view>
          <view>👤 检测部 收</view>
          <view>☎️ 400-xxx-xxxx</view>
          <button class="u-btn u-btn-primary u-btn--sm copy-btn" bindtap="copyAddress">复制地址</button>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="section">
        <view class="section-title">重要注意事项</view>
        <view class="section-block">
          <view class="item-text">• 快递单上务必注明检测号</view>
          <view class="item-text">• 建议使用顺丰/京东等快递</view>
          <view class="item-text">• 样品寄出后状态会自动更新</view>
          <view class="item-text">• 工作日寄出，避免周末滞留</view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <button class="u-btn u-btn-primary u-btn--md u-btn--pill u-btn-block" bindtap="confirmMailed">确认已邮寄</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

